{"tid":632705,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逾26萬中國司機獲免試簽發香港正式駕照　去年新增逾3.5萬人　交通意外率增25%","createTime":"2018-04-17T15:57:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T06:23:16.000Z","uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"21c76bd3fc6dc014042cfbf2b8e95aa0a2847f2a","tid":632705,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T15:57:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180416/58081518\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180416%2F58081518&d=ZZ14AsFCL0KwOAoEWLtLT8KJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=cabc8caa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180416%2F58081518&h=b93bd15e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180416/58081518</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180416/large/1523881349_28c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180416%2Flarge%2F1523881349_28c1.jpg&h=e72696da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 政府回覆立法會財委會的文件指出，2017年內新增35,765名內地司機獲免試簽發香港正式駕駛執照，而截至2017年底，總共有436,877名外地司機獲免試簽發香港正式駕駛執照，當中六成，共267,476名為內地司機。<br />\n<br />\n文件表示，以免試簽發方式取得駕駛執照的駕駛人士涉及的交通意外數目近年上升了25%，當中2015年為376宗，2016年為462宗，2017年469宗。<br />\n<br />\n文件指出，凡獲免試簽發駕駛執照的人士，都會獲發一本運輸署的《道路使用者守則》， 列明適用於各類道路使用者的各種規則、指示及資料，並涵蓋不同道路和交通情況，以期加深外地司機對本港交通規則與規例的認識。"},{"pid":"609292735465dad72f1d85e3b3b9ae523836f8d3","tid":632705,"uid":3331,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T16:20:15.000Z","msg":"明顯係想拉低香港所有方面既quality balance返佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b199fad5eb522872d892684502a7998f8f737c3d","tid":632705,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T16:23:49.000Z","msg":"《道路使用者守則》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" clas